node.text:
I discovered the angel voice of @lizzymcalpine on Instagram last year, then I bumped into her in real life and we decided to meet up and try singing something together. 
(Wait until she releases her next album; she played me some of it… it will blow your mind!)

Anyway, of all the music in the world… she chose one of, if not my favourite ever song. 
The @bonnieraittofficial version of ’I Can’t Make you Love Me’ is responsible for more of my tears than any other musical recording ever. 

I hope this finds your heart healing, growing or bursting with love, magnetised to another
💔❤️‍🩹💚💗❤️

For anyone not able to be with their loved ones today,
For anyone who has struggled this year, 
For anyone not feeling quite yourself today,
For anyone trying their best,
For anyone putting on a brave face,
For anyone missing someone,
For anyone saying, ‘F%#* it, I’m gonna enjoy some Christmas cheer today, dammit!’
For anyone & everyone because I’m sure you’re at least one of these... I hope you squeeze whatever joy there is to be squeezed out of today: the only Christmas Day 2020 there will ever be!
All my love, BB
❤️

“I'm jealous of the rain
That falls upon your skin
It's closer than my hands have been
I'm jealous of the rain

I'm jealous of the wind
That ripples through your clothes
It's closer than your shadow
Oh, I'm jealous of the wind

I'm jealous of the nights
That I don't spend with you
I'm wondering who you lay next to
Oh, I'm jealous of the nights

Cause I wished you the best of all this world could give
And I told you when you left me
There's nothing to forgive

But I always thought you'd come back
Tell me all you found was heartbreak and misery
It's hard for me to say
I'm jealous of the way
You're happy without me”

🎹💗

node.text:
I discovered the angel voice of @lizzymcalpine on Instagram last year, then I bumped into her in real life and we decided to meet up and try singing something together. 
(Wait until she releases her next album; she played me some of it… it will blow your mind!)

Anyway, of all the music in the world… she chose one of, if not my favourite ever song. 
The @bonnieraittofficial version of ’I Can’t Make you Love Me’ is responsible for more of my tears than any other musical recording ever. 

I hope this finds your heart healing, growing or bursting with love, magnetised to another
💔❤️‍🩹💚💗❤️
